name: Dark World
author: Eternal
notes: As long as I didn't brick I destroyed everything including SSA and sylvans. In my experience I would have my combo first turn a lot of the time.  Sylvans were easy since most of the time they just set 1 monster and end, at that point it's a free win. At one point I had 4 OTK's in a row vs sylvans before getting cucked on kog rank up. If you brick it's basically over.
